@node "1" "What is it?"

@{jcenter}

@{u}That is it:@{uu}@{line}
@{line}
This is a mounlist for the 270MB Drives.@{line}

@endnode

@node "2" "What is needed?"

@{jcenter}

@{u}This is needed:@{uu}@{line}
@{line}
Amiga with A-OS 2.0 or higher.@{line}
A SyQuest 270MB Drive.@{line}

@endnode

@node "3" "Importend!"

@{u}Importend:@{uu}@{line}
@{line}
It's not sure that this mounlist will work with SyQuest disk, wich are created like a harddisk.@{line}

@endnode

@node "4" "How to use it?"

@{b}Use it like this:@{ub}@{line}
@{line}
Copy the Mountlist to Devs:DOSDrivers to mount it automticaly.@{line}
If you want a manual mount so copy it to Storage/DOSDrivers or elswhere.@{line}
@{line}
After that change in the tooltypes of the icon the device and the unit to your drive.@{line}

@endnode

